                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>of our Holy Religion, and in which I<lb/> may find out when the holy days\n                    <sic>ocur</sic>.<lb/> and if you have a small cheap Bible<lb/> you may send it,\n                    <sic>thease</sic> book my dear<lb/> sir you may send either by express or<lb/>\n                mail as you may think best and<lb/> sending the bill to <persName>Mr\n                    Mayer</persName> it will<lb/> meet prompt payment, by attending<lb/> to this\n                most Rev Sir you will confer<lb/> a Great favor. I remain yours</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(9)\">Most Respectfully</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Nathan E. Levy</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>address</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Master <persName role=\"author\">Nathan E. Levy</persName>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Georgetown College</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">\n                <placeName>Georgetown D. C.</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p>you may also enclose me a bill and your Catalogue<lb/> you will <sic>allso</sic> send\n                me a couple of Good<lb/> instructive reading books, <persName role=\"author\"\n                    >NEL</persName></p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3br8n26c/canvas/p2"
                }
